			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2266016">
									

<p>The use of feet in the faux-SCP document kills me, and I felt like there were way too many sentences in a row in the beginning that essentially starts with &quot;He did&quot; or &quot;He says&quot; etc. You also don't need the heading at the top. You already have it as the tale title.</p>
<p>On the whole though, it's nice, and I'm amused by it, and the characterization of Foxx. It's<br />
really nice to see Skitter Marshall here too and how he interacts with others. This is close to an upvote, but all the issues in the first paragraph stop me from it (the repetition of &quot;He&quot; the most.)</p>
<p>EDIT: Upon seeing the revisions, +1.</p>

